CSS
=> Cascading Style sheet
=> This is used to style the HTML Webpages

CSS can be implemented in 3 approaches
    Inline
    Internal
    External

CSS Selectors
    Element
    Attribute
        id 
        class
    Group
    Universal
    Pseudo(Ur Own Task)
    child

CSS Colors
    Standard Colors
    rgb
    rgba
    3 digit Hexadecimal
    6 decimal Hexadecimal
    HSL - Hue Saturation Lightness(Ur Own Task) => 120*120*120 => 3.5 million

