CSS Directions
clockwise direction => top right bottom left (Shorthand property)

Background
    => background-color 
    => background-image 
            url('location')
    => background-video****
    => background-repeat 

Box Model
    Margin
        margin: 10px;
        Here the 10px was occupied in all the 4 Directions

        margin-top
        margin-right
        margin-bottom
        margin-left

        margin: top right bottom left;
        margin: 200px 100px 200px 100px;

        margin :10 px;

        margin: 50px 100px;

        50px - y axis -> top to botom
        100px - x axis -> left to right

        margin: 10px 20px 15px;

    Padding
        padding: 10px;
        Here the 10px was occupied in all the 4 Directions

        padding-top
        padding-right
        padding-bottom
        padding-left

        padding: top right bottom left;
        padding: 200px 100px 200px 100px;

